Hello,
I am currently testing some stuff with ML.NET, specifically Binary Logistic Regression, and trying to get CL to work on that.
To do that I found a few different articles, mainly [this one](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/machine-learning/how-to-guides/retrain-model-ml-net), which I followed as closely as the algorithm allowed.
However when trying to get the parameters from a loaded model, and matching that to ``LinearRegressionModelParameters``, it just returns ``null`` despite previously having data.

This is how I save my model and pipeline:
```cs
