I have seen in the article I mentioned that the algorithms have different parameter outputs, but cant seem to find the correct one for ``LbfgsLogisticRegression`` 
only thing I found was the one I am currently using, which doesn't work for me, so it seems like I either missed something, or made a mistake in my implementation. Can anyone help me with this?

